cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.NE

The paper presents a method for generating novel drug-like molecules using a deep neural network, specifically a long short-term memory (LSTM) network. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The generation of molecules also involves the use of chemical databases and cheminformatics techniques, which could be classified under databases (cs.DB) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE). Finally, the use of neural networks for generating molecules is a common application of deep learning in chemistry, which could be classified under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
